Django: is module for web development
=========================================
Django : is framwork to develop the ui

How to setup the environment?
	pip install django 
	
Editor
	VSCode 
			https://code.visualstudio.com/download
	Eclipse
	Spyder
	PyCharm
	Atom
	Subline
	etc.. 

Create DJango Project
=========================
python "C:\Python27\Scripts\django-admin.py" startproject ds  
	-- here ds is name of the project


Structure of the project
===========================
ds
	ds
		__init__.py
		settings.py
		urls.py
		wsgi.py		
	manage.py			1.


Build and run the project
=================================
cd ds		--change directory (go inside project folder)
python manage.py runserver 

--stop the project
ctlr+c  : cancel or stop the project

Create Aplication inside Project
======================================
python "C:\Python27\Scripts\django-admin.py" startapp visualization  

Project vs Application 
	Project	: is collection of application 
		: project also known suite 
		: example - ms office 
	Application  : building block of task for respective business objective
		: example - excel, powerpoint  etc.


App Structure
====================
views.py
		def index(request):
			return HttpResponse("Hey, this is first app ")
models.py
admin.py
app.py...

